snippet.title: Playing Every Apple II Floppy, E74 - Autobahn
snippet.description:
Taking a quick look at Autobahn, a 1981 release for the Apple II.

This is episode 74 of Woz A Day, my series where I'm taking a look at Apple II software in the "WOZ" disk image format uploaded to the Internet Archive "Woz A Day" collection in upload order: https://archive.org/details/wozaday
These are preservation-quality unmodified/uncracked disk images that can pass copy-protection checks and preserve the original "retail" experience.

📋 Woz A Day Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLXVtlqgyC7v2ACowTpMXcMrLbfX1qdBHE
💾 Download disk image or play in-browser: https://archive.org/details/wozaday_Autobahn

Other Woz A Day videos for games by this developer:
Phantoms Five: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3OJ5jf993Rs
Space Eggs: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ONvBFjQErNY
